Hi everyone,

Probably, this is gonna be some kind of strange question, but I'm completely lost so, if anyone can help, thanks in advance.
I've been developing an application that works with xlsx files. In my local server everything worked fine, but the problem was when I tested it in a remote server.
After execution, in local server I get full message on screen: PHPExcel_Shared_String CI_ExcelMY_ExcelPHP.... but in remote server, there's something missing at the end of the string: "PHPExcel_Worksheet_AutoFilter_ColumnPHPExcel_Calculation_Token_Stack" doesn't appear.

By the way, local server works with php5.3.3 and remote server with php5.3.10
I would appreciate any help.

Thanks!
